<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
    <title>长沙优步一周年辣，热辣红包快来抢辣！</title>
    <script src="vendor/lib-flexible/build/flexible.js"></script>
    <script src="vendor/zepto/zepto.min.js"></script>
    <link href="css/changsha.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen">
</head>
<body>
<div id="wx_pic" style="display: none;margin: 0 auto;">
    <img src="images/changsha/topic3.png"/>
</div>
<div class="wrap-page">
    <section class="page flex-m" id="page1" style="display: none;">

        <div class="inner" style="padding-bottom:0 0 1.25rem 0;">

            <img src="images/changsha/topic.png" alt="" style="width: 100%;margin-bottom: 0.3125rem">
            <p class="s-info" style="margin-bottom: 0.3125rem;color: #ffffff;">关注微信公众号</p>
            <p class="l-info" style="margin-bottom: 0.3125rem;color: #ffffff;font-size: 20px;">"进击的臭豆腐"</p>
            <p class="s-info" style="color: #ffffff;">更多热辣资讯!</p>
            <!--<button class="com-btn" style="margin-top: 0.46875rem">点击直达</button>-->
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="page flex-m" id="page2" style="background: #0e1b45;display: none;">
        <div class="inner">
            <p class="l-info1 text-left">推荐乘客<br>再获三次免费行程</p>

            <div class="flex-box flex-d img-lst">
                <div class="left-img text-left"><img src="images/changsha/pic1.png" alt=""></div>
                <div class="flex-1 text-left">
                    <p class="num">1</p>
                    <p class="s-info1">打开Uber APP<br>
                        选择"<span class="r-span">推荐乘客得优惠</span>"<br>将您的优惠码分享给好友
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-box flex-d img-lst">

                <div class="left-img text-left"><img src="images/changsha/pic2.png" alt=""></div>
                <div class="flex-1 text-left">
                    <p class="num">2</p>
                    <p class="s-info1">好友注册成功后<span class="r-span">输入您的优惠码</span>并完成首次乘车
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-box flex-d img-lst">
                <div class="left-img text-left"><img src="images/changsha/pic3.png" alt=""></div>
                <div class="flex-1 text-left">
                    <p class="num">3</p>
                    <p class="s-info1">您的帐户将获得<span class="r-span">3次10元</span>乘车优惠 可在"付款"中查看
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="com-btn" style="margin-top: 0.46875rem;width: 5.65625rem;font-size: 18px;" onclick="$('#page2').hide();$('#page1').show();" >我要分享给好友</button>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="page flex-m" id="page3" style="background: #0e1b45;display:none;">
        <div class="inner">
            <img src="images/changsha/topic1.png" style="width: 6.28125rem" alt="" class="topic">
            <p class="l-info" style="color: #f90052;font-size: 28px;">优步长沙一周年辣</p>
            <p class="l-info" style="color: #f90052;font-size: 28px;">15次72折红包</p>                                                                       
            <p class="s-info" style="margin-top: 0.625rem;color: #ffffff;">可享15次72折行程,封顶4元</p>
            <p class="s-info" style="color: #ffffff;">5月29日前,长沙地区使用人民优步有效</p>
            <p class="s-info" style="color: #ffffff;">使用此红包,可享拼车最低36折!</p>

            <button class="com-btn" style="margin-top: 0.46875rem" onclick="$('#page3').hide();$('#page2').show();">教你获取更多乘车金</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page flex-m" id="page4" style="display:none;">
        <div class="inner">
            <img src="images/changsha/topic2.png" alt="" style="width: 7.9375rem">
            <p class="m-info" style="margin-top:0.625rem;margin-bottom: 0.78125rem;color: #ffffff;">输入优步注册手机号码<br>马上热辣辣抢红包!</p>

            <input type="text" class="ipt" placeholder="请输入手机号码" id="phoneNumber">

            <button class="com-btn" style="width: 5.5rem" id="phone_btn" onclick="phoneCoupon()">立即抢红包</button>
            <input type="hidden" id="carCouponId"/>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page flex-m" id="page5" style="display: none;">
        <img src="images/changsha/logo.png" alt="" class="logo">
        <img src="images/changsha/topic3.png" alt="" style="width: 100%;margin-top:1.5625rem" onclick="$('#page5').hide();$('#page4').show();">


    </section>
    <section class="page flex-m" id="page6" style="display: none;">
        <div class="inner">

            <img src="images/changsha/topic4.png" class="topic" style="width: 9rem">
            <button class="com-btn" style="width: 6.375rem" onclick="window.location.href='https://get.uber.com.cn/invite/csoneyearh5new'">马上注册抢红包</button>
        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="page flex-m" id="page7" style="display: none;">
        <div class="inner">

            <p class="m-info" style="margin-bottom: 0.78125rem">请分享您的心情！</p>

            <textarea class="ipt" rows="8" style="height: 90px;margin-top: 5px" placeholder="请写下你的心情"></textarea>
            <div></div>
            <button class="com-btn">确定</button>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery-1.7.2.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../javascript/av-0.5.1.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../javascript/AV.analytics.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../javascript/event.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../javascript/common.js"></script>
<script src="vendor/lib-flexible/build/flexible.js"></script>
<script src="vendor/zepto/zepto.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/index.js"></script>
</body>

</html>